articles.title: Trump discussed nuclear submarines with Australian billionaire Anthony Pratt, three sources say - CBS News
articles.description: Trump allegedly discussed sensitive information pertaining to American nuclear submarines with an Australian billionaire at his Mar-a-Lago resort, according to three people familiar with the matter.
